Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:03.60,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(50,494)}{\frz270}僕は　貴方を　忘れない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:10.06,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(50,494)}{\frz270}時の音導く　雨雲の先
