Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:10.06,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(1874,494)}{\frz270}时间的声音会指引　越过雨云
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:15.73,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(1874,494)}{\frz270}终将在那片海
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:22.45,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(1874,494)}{\frz270}微笑着和你相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:27.64,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(1874,494)}{\frz270}我们共同活过的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:33.74,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(1874,494)}{\frz270}这一定是个　醒不来的梦
